      "date": "2013-05-22 08:58:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(10 inline comments)\n\nTo be honest, this patch is very difficult to inspect since it is so large.\n\nIt would be a lot easier if it were split into a couple of smaller parts, namely splitting mdd_lfsck.c into separate files within the mdd/ directory (i.e. without any code changes at all), then patch it to make it independent from the MDD code, and finally move it into the separate lfsck/ directory.\n\nAs it was, I did some visual comparison after downloading the patch against the original code, but even this is difficult since the functions have moved into different files.",
