          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-05-28 05:12:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 8:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/62053a6a-c752-11e2-ae6b-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
